    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund free or heavily discounted solar panels for community leisure centres",
        "additional_details": "We believe our leisure centres are struggling with the energy crisis to heat pools and run air conditioning systems, and as a result many are closing or having to increase prices which can make it unaffordable for people. \r\n \r\nMany of these leisure centres could have large carbon footprints, encouraging them to use solar panels could also help the government reach their net zero carbon targets whilst securing the health of its society.\r\n \r\nPlease help us to help ourselves and don\u2019t let\u2019s these gems of the community fall into ruin.\r\n",
        "background": "Provide funding to enable community leisure centres to apply for free (or heavily discounted solar panels).",
